 da ja pitam u Monaku, toga sigurno nema.

1296
01:25:36,700 --> 01:25:37,540
 Ali ima.

1297
01:25:37,540 --> 01:25:38,640
 U Monaku toga nema.

1298
01:25:38,640 --> 01:25:41,060
 Međutim, ima svugdje drugdje.

1299
01:25:41,060 --> 01:25:43,620
 Ima u Italiju, u Francuskoj, u Engleskoj,

1300
01:25:43,620 --> 01:25:44,860
 u Belgiji, u Švedskoj,

1301
01:25:44,860 --> 01:25:45,800
 u Norveškoj, svugdje.

1302
01:25:45,800 --> 01:25:50,480
 I to se nema ni u Mađarskoj.

1303
01:25:50,480 --> 01:25:52,540
 Ali ako padne Orban,

1304
01:25:52,540 --> 01:25:53,520
 bit će i u Mađarskoj.

1305
01:25:53,520 --> 01:25:54,300
 A hoće li pasti?

1306
01:25:54,300 --> 01:25:55,780
 Ne znam.

1307
01:25:56,320 --> 01:25:58,540
 Šta vam nos vaš kaže?

1308
01:25:58,540 --> 01:26:01,900
 50% ili hoće ili neće.

1309
01:26:01,900 --> 01:26:05,760
 Sad nećete bubnuti župa.

1310
01:26:05,760 --> 01:26:08,780
 Gledajte, imamo ove tu

1311
01:26:08,780 --> 01:26:10,880
 ispitivanja javnog mijenja,

1312
01:26:10,880 --> 01:26:13,120
 ali ispitivanja javnog mijenja

1313
01:26:13,120 --> 01:26:15,420
 će dati šta naručitelj želi da da.

1314
01:26:15,420 --> 01:26:17,960
 Tako da ne možemo vjerovat šta se tamo.

1315
01:26:17,960 --> 01:26:19,600
 Meni je sad teško uopće

1316
01:26:19,600 --> 01:26:21,520
 pojmiti da bi Mađari

1317
01:26:21,520 --> 01:26:23,460
 mogli izazvati ovoga

1318
01:26:23,460 --> 01:26:24,560
 Mađara.

1319
01:26:25,160 --> 01:26:28,080
 jer šta bi onda...

1320
01:26:28,080 --> 01:26:29,540
 Koji vodi u svim anketama.

1321
01:26:29,540 --> 01:26:32,060
 Koji navodno vodi u svim anketama.

1322
01:26:32,060 --> 01:26:33,800
 Ano je ključna riječ navodno.

1323
01:26:33,800 --> 01:26:36,780
 Dajte, znači, šta su se sad Mađari

1324
01:26:36,780 --> 01:26:39,020
 na jedan put domisluje da bi oni ipak želili

1325
01:26:39,020 --> 01:26:40,500
 da im je zemlja preplavljena

1326
01:26:40,500 --> 01:26:43,520
 migrantima, da imaju LGBT parade.

1327
01:26:46,220 --> 01:26:48,000
 Ali možda im je dosta već orbana.

1328
01:26:48,000 --> 01:26:50,600
 Možda im je dosta, ne znam kako kažu, korupcije.

1329
01:26:50,600 --> 01:26:52,620
 Nemam pojma.

1330
01:26:52,620 --> 01:26:53,480
 Evo pa sad imate

1331
01:26:53,480 --> 01:26:55,320
 Mađarska i Slovačka

1332
01:26:55,320 --> 01:26:56,820
 vode energetski rat.

1333
01:26:56,820 --> 01:26:58,220
 Mislim da sam to rekla na početku.

1334
01:26:58,220 --> 01:27:01,140
 Odnosno naftni rat, sukob sa Ukrajinom.

1335
01:27:01,140 --> 01:27:05,900
 Tu je nekako i Hrvatska upletena

1336
01:27:05,900 --> 01:27:07,020
 zbog našeg Janafa.

1337
01:27:07,020 --> 01:27:09,180
 Rekla je danas Evropska komisija

1338
01:27:09,180 --> 01:27:11,200
 da neka Hrvatska sama odluči

1339
01:27:11,200 --> 01:27:16,100
 hoće li sirovu rusku naftu

1340
01:27:16,100 --> 01:27:18,700
 kroz naš Janaf distribuirati.

1341
01:27:18,700 --> 01:27:21,520
 Da si sprljamo naš naftovod

1342
01:27:21,520 --> 01:27:22,940
 sa ruskom naftom, a nikad.

1343
01:27:22,940 --> 01:27:25,660
 Najšalni se, naravno.

1344
01:27:25,660 --> 01:27:27,160
 Gledajte, ja ne znam,

1345
01:27:27,160 --> 01:27:29,420
 jer šta bi to značilo

1346
01:27:29,420 --> 01:27:31,100
 da onda Mađari žele odustati

1347
01:27:31,100 --> 01:27:32,100
 od svoje pozicije,

1348
01:27:32,100 --> 01:27:33,320
 od svog suvereniteta

1349
01:27:33,320 --> 01:27:34,660
 zato što ih ovi ucijenjuju.

1350
01:27:34,660 --> 01:27:38,700
 A oni su susjedi sa Ukrajinom.

1351
01:27:38,700 --> 01:27:40,740
 Znači, ako se rat proširi,

1352
01:27:40,740 --> 01:27:43,820
 prvo će zahvatiti

1353
01:27:43,820 --> 01:27:45,800
 susjedne zemlje Ukrajine,

1354
01:27:45,800 --> 01:27:48,580
 među njima i Mađarsku,

1355
01:27:48,580 --> 01:27:52,640
 a u Mađarskoj se već Ukrajina

1356
01:27:52,640 --> 01:27:55,280
 zlostavlja mađarsku manjinu.

1357
01:27:55,280 --> 01:27:58,200
 I već su tu

1358
01:27:58,200 --> 01:28:02,280
 po malo kipi

1359
01:28:02,280 --> 01:28:06,340
 sukob između te dvije strane.

1360
01:28:06,340 --> 01:28:09,240
 I sad, koja je reakcija

1361
01:28:09,240 --> 01:28:11,100
 običnog naroda na to da kaže

1362
01:28:11,100 --> 01:28:13,540
 pa dobro, pritišću nas,

1363
01:28:13,540 --> 01:28:15,900
 ajde, ajde, ajde, ajmo se pustiti.

1364
01:28:15,900 --> 01:28:17,360
 Ajmo odustati.

1365
01:28:17,360 --> 01:28:21,960
 Prekinuli su nam dovod nafte

1366
01:28:21,960 --> 01:28:23,520
 zato što im nećemo da,

1367
01:28:23,520 --> 01:28:26,040
 ne znam koliko milijardi...

1368
01:28:26,040 --> 01:28:29,860
 90 milijardi eura je blokirala

1369
01:28:29,860 --> 01:28:30,600
 zbog toga, Mađarska.

1370
01:28:30,600 --> 01:28:32,880
 90 milijardi nije to sve od Mađara,

1371
01:28:32,880 --> 01:28:34,180
 jedan dio od Mađara, ali...

1372
01:28:34,180 --> 01:28:37,080
 Znači, sve te zavrzlame

1373
01:28:37,080 --> 01:28:40,000
 raste pritisak na Mađarsku

1374
01:28:40,000 --> 01:28:42,960
 i sad, ajmo odustati od sebe

1375
01:28:42,960 --> 01:28:45,000
 da bi mogli imati

1376
01:28:45,000 --> 01:28:48,100
 LGBT parade i imigrante

1377
01:28:48,100 --> 01:28:50,440
 i da nam dolazi nafta.

1378
01:28:50,440 --> 01:28:52,920
 Ja ne znam, ovaj...

1379
01:28:52,920 --> 01:28:54,960
 Tako da, meni je...

1380
01:28:54,960 --> 01:28:57,060
 Ne znam čitati Mađarsku,

1381
01:28:57,060 --> 01:29:00,080
 ne znam kako bi javno raspoloženje

1382
01:29:00,080 --> 01:29:01,220
 unutar Mađarske

1383
01:29:01,220 --> 01:29:04,840
 interpretirao,

1384
01:29:04,840 --> 01:29:07,460
 ali šta dolazi kroz...

1385
01:29:07,460 --> 01:29:11,300
 Šta dolazi kroz ove javne medije,

1386
01:29:11,300 --> 01:29:12,640
 to ne vjerujem ništa.

1387
01:29:12,740 --> 01:29:15,340
 Više sam sklon da suprotno mislim

1388
01:29:15,340 --> 01:29:16,740
 od onoga što nam serviraju.

1389
01:29:16,740 --> 01:29:18,380
 Neka Mađari sami odluče

1390
01:29:18,380 --> 01:29:19,340
 o svojoj sudbini.

1391
01:29:19,340 --> 01:29:21,680
 Pa, naravno, zato što smo

1392
01:29:21,680 --> 01:29:22,760
 nije demokracija

1393
01:29:22,760 --> 01:29:24,500
 i mi držimo do ljudskih prava

1394
01:29:24,500 --> 01:29:27,500
 i parlamentarnog...

1395
01:29:27,500 --> 01:29:29,140
 Kako se to već zove.

1396
01:29:29,140 --> 01:29:30,140
 Sve te ljepe stvari.

1397
01:29:30,140 --> 01:29:32,000
 Koliko pratite, gospodine Krajner,

1398
01:29:32,000 --> 01:29:33,160
 događanja u Hrvatskoj?

1399
01:29:33,160 --> 01:29:38,320
 Pa, uglavnom, površno i malo

1400
01:29:38,320 --> 01:29:41,200
 i uglavnom kada sam u Hrvatskoj.

1401
01:29:41,280 --> 01:29:42,680
 jer onda neizbježno

1402
01:29:42,680 --> 01:29:44,920
 to vidimo u novinama

1403
01:29:44,920 --> 01:29:48,260
 i na televiziji i tako dalje.

1404
01:29:48,260 --> 01:29:51,880
 I ono što me svaki put malo iznenadi

1405
01:29:51,880 --> 01:29:53,960
 je da mi joj živimo u 40-im godinama.

1406
01:29:53,960 --> 01:29:56,220
 Jer se neprestano govori

1407
01:29:56,220 --> 01:29:57,880
 o Ustašama i Četmicima.

1408
01:29:57,880 --> 01:30:01,540
 To mi je baš malo mutno.

1409
01:30:01,720 --> 01:30:06,060
 zašto smo toliko obsjednuti

1410
01:30:06,060 --> 01:30:09,300
 pitanjima koje više ne možemo riješiti.

1411
01:30:09,300 --> 01:30:11,800
 Znate, ušao sam u polemiku

1412
01:30:11,800 --> 01:30:15,440
 s jednim čovjekom na internetu

1413
01:30:15,440 --> 01:30:17,120
 preko e-maila.

1414
01:30:19,120 --> 01:30:22,560
 ovako malo, rekuo bi da malo mi je desničario

1415
01:30:22,560 --> 01:30:24,840
 po uporukama.

1416
01:30:24,840 --> 01:30:27,800
 I sad,

1417
01:30:27,800 --> 01:30:32,380
 ja sam spomenuo, pa nismo baš u jako dobroj situaciji.

1418
01:30:32,380 --> 01:30:33,640
 Sad nam je prva,

1419
01:30:33,640 --> 01:30:36,720
 najveća manjina u Hrvatskoj su nam

1420
01:30:36,720 --> 01:30:39,380
 Hindusi, Indici i Nepalci.

1421
01:30:39,380 --> 01:30:41,380
 To nije,

1422
01:30:41,380 --> 01:30:43,260
 mislim,

1423
01:30:43,260 --> 01:30:44,300
 šta god,

1424
01:30:44,300 --> 01:30:47,140
 kakav god čovjek imao stav prema Srbima,

1425
01:30:47,140 --> 01:30:48,180
 Srbi su ipak

1426
01:30:48,180 --> 01:30:51,560
 isti jezik govorimo,

1427
01:30:51,560 --> 01:30:53,120
 isto izgledamo.

1428
01:30:53,120 --> 01:30:55,620
 Kršćani su.

1429
01:30:55,620 --> 01:30:59,900
 Ako nam nije kultura ista,

1430
01:30:59,900 --> 01:31:00,760
 vrlo je slična.

1431
01:31:00,760 --> 01:31:01,680
 Razumijemo se.

1432
01:31:01,680 --> 01:31:04,200
 I ovdje su stoljećima.

1433
01:31:04,200 --> 01:31:05,880
 I napali su nas.

1434
01:31:06,720 --> 01:31:08,060
 gamovinski rat.

1435
01:31:08,060 --> 01:31:11,180
 Da, napali su nas.

1436
01:31:11,180 --> 01:31:12,340
 Znate, to je,

1437
01:31:12,340 --> 01:31:15,140
 u Hrvatskoj kolektivnoj svijesti

1438
01:31:15,140 --> 01:31:17,720
 je to pečat koji...

1439
01:31:17,720 --> 01:31:18,920
 To se kad desilo?

1440
01:31:18,920 --> 01:31:20,180
 Prije 30 godina.

1441
01:31:20,180 --> 01:31:22,740
 A oni su tu stoljećima.

1442
01:31:22,740 --> 01:31:25,160
 I zašto su nas napali?

1443
01:31:25,160 --> 01:31:27,060
 Jer ih je neko

1444
01:31:27,060 --> 01:31:28,900
 na to nahuškao.

1445
01:31:28,900 --> 01:31:30,520
 A to,

1446
01:31:30,520 --> 01:31:32,960
 trebamo biti svjesni

1447
01:31:32,960 --> 01:31:34,780
 da to se

1448
01:31:34,780 --> 01:31:36,700
 uvijek i stalno dešava

1449
01:31:36,700 --> 01:31:37,380
 u svijetu.

1450
01:31:37,380 --> 01:31:38,660
 Znači, ako neko želi

1451
01:31:38,660 --> 01:31:40,660
 destabilizirati neki prostor,

1452
01:31:40,660 --> 01:31:42,160
 uzeti će neku manjinu,

1453
01:31:42,160 --> 01:31:48,840
 napunit će ih strahom

1454
01:31:48,840 --> 01:31:50,860
 i nahuškat će ih

1455
01:31:50,860 --> 01:31:53,160
 da krenu

1456
01:31:53,160 --> 01:31:54,160
 u sukobe.

1457
01:31:54,160 --> 01:31:56,160
 Znači,

1458
01:31:56,160 --> 01:31:57,580
 tako je počeo,

1459
01:31:57,580 --> 01:31:58,500
 tako je recimo

1460
01:31:58,500 --> 01:31:59,460
 drugi svjetski rat

1461
01:31:59,460 --> 01:32:00,520
 u Češkoj počeo.

1462
01:32:00,620 --> 01:32:04,960
 Hitler je krenuo

1463
01:32:04,960 --> 01:32:06,160
 nahuškavati

1464
01:32:06,160 --> 01:32:07,880
 ove njemce,

1465
01:32:07,880 --> 01:32:08,640
 sudete,

1466
01:32:08,640 --> 01:32:10,040
 protiv Češke.

1467
01:32:10,040 --> 01:32:12,120
 I onda,

1468
01:32:12,120 --> 01:32:13,320
 takve iste stvari

1469
01:32:13,320 --> 01:32:14,160
 vam se dešavaju

1470
01:32:14,160 --> 01:32:15,840
 između Grka i Turaka,

1471
01:32:15,840 --> 01:32:17,540
 između Armenaca

1472
01:32:17,540 --> 01:32:18,900
 i Azerbejdžanaca,

1473
01:32:18,900 --> 01:32:21,640
 između Kineza i Japanaca.

1474
01:32:22,640 --> 01:32:25,980
 To nije neko neprijateljstvo

1475
01:32:25,980 --> 01:32:27,260
 koje postoji tamo

1476
01:32:27,260 --> 01:32:29,700
 zato što je to neizbježno tako,

1477
01:32:29,700 --> 01:32:31,660
 zato što se ti ljudi

1478
01:32:31,660 --> 01:32:34,520
 onako neiskorjenjivo mrze,

1479
01:32:34,520 --> 01:32:36,220
 nego je to

1480
01:32:36,220 --> 01:32:39,660
 hotimično iscenirano

1481
01:32:39,660 --> 01:32:40,160
 izvana.

1482
01:32:40,160 --> 01:32:42,160
 Znate, govorili smo ono i...

1483
01:32:42,160 --> 01:32:43,240
 Prvi put ste to kod mene

1484
01:32:43,240 --> 01:32:44,860
 rekli, staklenke i mrave.

1485
01:32:44,860 --> 01:32:47,220
 Staklenke sa crvenim i crvim mravima.

1486
01:32:47,220 --> 01:32:49,340
 Znači, mravi se ne napadaju

1487
01:32:49,340 --> 01:32:50,640
 dok neko tu staklenku

1488
01:32:50,640 --> 01:32:52,920
 dobro ne potrese.

1489
01:32:52,920 --> 01:32:54,640
 E sad, znači mi,

1490
01:32:54,640 --> 01:32:57,760
 umjesto da smo psjednuti Srbima,

1491
01:32:57,760 --> 01:32:59,820
 mi bi trebali biti psjednuti

1492
01:32:59,820 --> 01:33:01,360
 ko nam trese staklenku.

1493
01:33:01,360 --> 01:33:03,520
 Jer kako su nam je potresli

1494
01:33:03,520 --> 01:33:04,560
 između nas i Srba,

1495
01:33:04,560 --> 01:33:06,120
 mogu sutra je potresti

1496
01:33:06,120 --> 01:33:07,820
 između Hrvata i tih Indijaca

1497
01:33:07,820 --> 01:33:08,540
 i Nepalaca.

1498
01:33:08,540 --> 01:33:14,260
 I tako da

1499
01:33:14,260 --> 01:33:17,040
 mi radi svoje budućnosti

1500
01:33:17,040 --> 01:33:18,020
 i svoje sigurnosti

1501
01:33:18,020 --> 01:33:19,020
 moramo tim stvarima

1502
01:33:19,020 --> 01:33:20,200
 voditi računa,

1503
01:33:20,400 --> 01:33:21,820
 a ne se povoditi

1504
01:33:21,820 --> 01:33:23,520
 za...

1505
01:33:23,520 --> 01:33:29,520
 znači, povoditi se ljenim razmišljanjem,

1506
01:33:29,520 --> 01:33:35,460
 emocionalnim nekakvim obsesijama

1507
01:33:35,460 --> 01:33:39,660
 i impulzivnim reakcijama.

1508
01:33:40,520 --> 01:33:42,480
 znači, ako vam je neko tu

1509
01:33:42,480 --> 01:33:44,420
 koji dijeli vašu kulturu,

1510
01:33:44,420 --> 01:33:45,620
 koji govori vaš jezik,

1511
01:33:45,620 --> 01:33:46,860
 koji izgleda isto kao vi

1512
01:33:46,860 --> 01:33:48,140
 i sa kojima ste

1513
01:33:48,140 --> 01:33:50,640
 ono isprepleteni stoljećima

1514
01:33:50,640 --> 01:33:52,140
 mješanih brakova i svega,

1515
01:33:52,140 --> 01:33:53,360
 mislim, šta zna, ja sam Hrvat,

1516
01:33:53,940 --> 01:33:57,560
 moja obitelj je dolazi od svuda pomalo,

1517
01:33:57,560 --> 01:34:00,160
 iz Slovenije i iz Češke,

1518
01:34:00,160 --> 01:34:04,320
 i iz Italije i iz Srbije i iz Dalmacije.

1519
01:34:04,860 --> 01:34:05,940
 i znači, ja ako idem

1520
01:34:05,940 --> 01:34:07,480
 tri, četiri generacije,

1521
01:34:07,480 --> 01:34:09,300
 moje Hrvatstvo je biti

1522
01:34:09,300 --> 01:34:12,640
 moj nekakav kulturni identitet.

1523
01:34:13,340 --> 01:34:15,720
 meni da neko ide brojat krvna zrca,

1524
01:34:15,720 --> 01:34:17,520
 ja ne znam šta bi izašlo van.

1525
01:34:17,520 --> 01:34:18,400
 Šta bi našao, jel da?

1526
01:34:18,400 --> 01:34:19,700
 Ali pretpostavljam da je tako

1527
01:34:19,700 --> 01:34:21,340
 za velik dio Hrvatstva,

1528
01:34:21,340 --> 01:34:23,240
 jer ovdje je prolazilo,

1529
01:34:23,240 --> 01:34:24,740
 prolazio je Napoleon

1530
01:34:24,740 --> 01:34:25,880
 sa svojim vojskama,

1531
01:34:25,880 --> 01:34:27,760
 Austro-Ugari, Italijani,

1532
01:34:27,760 --> 01:34:28,980
 Mlećani, Turci,

1533
01:34:28,980 --> 01:34:31,040
 svašto je tu bilo.

1534
01:34:31,040 --> 01:34:32,680
 Znači, ne možemo išći

1535
01:34:32,680 --> 01:34:33,720
 za krvnim zrcima,

1536
01:34:33,720 --> 01:34:35,960
 ali moramo uzimati kulturu

1537
01:34:35,960 --> 01:34:39,880
 kao nešto što stvara,

1538
01:34:39,880 --> 01:34:42,180
 što daje društvu

1539
01:34:42,180 --> 01:34:44,140
 kohezivnost je tako.

1540
01:34:44,140 --> 01:34:47,960
 I sad, ako ste jednu manjinu

1541
01:34:47,960 --> 01:34:48,900
 zamijenili nekom

1542
01:34:48,900 --> 01:34:51,440
 koja vam je to potpuno strano tijelo,

1543
01:34:51,440 --> 01:34:54,300
 čemu se možemo nadati s toga?

1544
01:34:54,300 --> 01:34:56,820
 Ne znam, ali možemo pogledati

1545
01:34:56,820 --> 01:34:57,780
 kako je u Molenbiku,

1546
01:34:57,780 --> 01:34:59,980
 kako je u Engleskoj

1547
01:34:59,980 --> 01:35:02,200
 sa tim Pakistancima što smo govorili,

1548
01:35:02,200 --> 01:35:03,800
 kako je u Švedskoj,

1549
01:35:03,800 --> 01:35:06,400
 kako je u Francuskoj,

1550
01:35:06,400 --> 01:35:08,140
 i nigdje nije dobro.

1551
01:35:08,140 --> 01:35:09,860
 Nigdje to nije izašlo na dobro.

1552
01:35:12,180 --> 01:35:13,760
 A opet, kažem, sa Srbima

1553
01:35:13,760 --> 01:35:15,000
 smo stoljećima skupa.

1554
01:35:16,140 --> 01:35:18,320
 i dio koji ne valja

1555
01:35:18,320 --> 01:35:20,720
 je otkad,

1556
01:35:20,720 --> 01:35:22,660
 reću vam kad je krenulo

1557
01:35:22,660 --> 01:35:23,240
 na Izbrdu.

1558
01:35:23,240 --> 01:35:29,240
 Kad smo išli

1559
01:35:29,240 --> 01:35:30,560
 ka Prvom svjetskom ratu,

1560
01:35:30,560 --> 01:35:32,600
 znači prije sto i toliko godina,

1561
01:35:32,600 --> 01:35:34,580
 onda su, šta je zna,

1562
01:35:34,660 --> 01:35:36,680
 Njemci su htjeli izgraditi

1563
01:35:36,680 --> 01:35:38,800
 prugu Berlin-Bagdad.

1564
01:35:38,800 --> 01:35:41,840
 Znači, htjeli su se povezati

1565
01:35:41,840 --> 01:35:44,240
 sa Zapadnom Azijom,

1566
01:35:44,240 --> 01:35:45,320
 s Bliskim Istokom,

1567
01:35:45,320 --> 01:35:46,740
 radi trgovine,

1568
01:35:46,740 --> 01:35:47,560
 radi razvoja,

1569
01:35:47,560 --> 01:35:50,560
 radi nafte i tako dalje.

1570
01:35:50,560 --> 01:35:52,460
 i onda su Britanci

1571
01:35:52,460 --> 01:35:54,220
 odlučili da

1572
01:35:54,220 --> 01:35:56,020
 Njemačku moraju

1573
01:35:56,020 --> 01:36:03,320
 sabit u svoj prostor.

1574
01:36:03,320 --> 01:36:04,780
 Malo srezat.

1575
01:36:04,780 --> 01:36:05,900
 Staviti u...

1576
01:36:05,900 --> 01:36:06,940
 Da, da, da.

1577
01:36:06,940 --> 01:36:08,940
 Kako se zove ono...

1578
01:36:08,940 --> 01:36:11,940
 Znači kad je stablo...

1579
01:36:11,940 --> 01:36:13,220
 Obrezat, orezat.

1580
01:36:13,220 --> 01:36:15,040
 Orezat, ne obrezat, orezat.

1581
01:36:15,040 --> 01:36:19,420
 I uglavnom, onda su htjeli im

1582
01:36:19,420 --> 01:36:21,420
 prekinuti tu prugu.

1583
01:36:21,420 --> 01:36:25,140
 I onda su ustanovili da je u biti

1584
01:36:25,140 --> 01:36:28,140
 ključni potez preko Srbije.

1585
01:36:28,140 --> 01:36:31,500
 I onda su, šta,

1586
01:36:31,500 --> 01:36:33,000
 odlučili su rušiti Njemačku

1587
01:36:33,000 --> 01:36:36,220
 i odlučili su rušiti Tursko carstvo.

1588
01:36:36,220 --> 01:36:37,320
 Otomansko.

1589
01:36:37,320 --> 01:36:38,060
 Da.

1590
01:36:38,060 --> 01:36:39,760
 I oni su onda,

1591
01:36:39,760 --> 01:36:42,600
 ušli su Britanci u Srbiju

1592
01:36:42,600 --> 01:36:43,940
 i tako su pokrenuli

1593
01:36:43,940 --> 01:36:45,000
 Balkanske ratove

1594
01:36:45,000 --> 01:36:47,060
 u kojima su Britanski časnici

1595
01:36:47,060 --> 01:36:48,800
 zapovjedali tu

1596
01:36:48,800 --> 01:36:50,540
 srpskim jedinicama.

1597
01:36:50,540 --> 01:36:53,280
 Znači oni su aktivno sudjelovali

1598
01:36:53,280 --> 01:36:53,740
 u tom,

1599
01:36:53,740 --> 01:36:55,880
 u tim Balkanskim ratovima

1600
01:36:55,880 --> 01:36:57,160
 da se,

1601
01:36:57,160 --> 01:36:59,600
 da se istjera van

1602
01:36:59,600 --> 01:37:03,040
 Osmanlijsko carstvo,

1603
01:37:03,040 --> 01:37:05,000
 da se Tursko carstvo istjera iz Srbije

1604
01:37:05,000 --> 01:37:07,820
 i da se prekine ta pruga,

1605
01:37:07,820 --> 01:37:10,000
 da se,

1606
01:37:10,000 --> 01:37:12,260
 da se Tursko carstvo i Njemačka povezu.

1607
01:37:12,640 --> 01:37:13,880
 onako ekonomski

1608
01:37:13,880 --> 01:37:16,180
 i znači da imaju tu neko

1609
01:37:16,180 --> 01:37:19,260
 neko savezništvo i suradnju.

1610
01:37:19,260 --> 01:37:22,240
 I oni su tu ušli u

1611
01:37:22,240 --> 01:37:25,100
 vojne i obavještajne strukture

1612
01:37:25,100 --> 01:37:26,480
 Srbije.

1613
01:37:27,760 --> 01:37:29,380
 i mislim da do dana današnjeg

1614
01:37:29,380 --> 01:37:30,580
 nisu izašli iz toga.

1615
01:37:30,580 --> 01:37:32,880
 Da oni i do dana i današnjeg

1616
01:37:32,880 --> 01:37:34,740
 kultiviraju te veze

1617
01:37:34,740 --> 01:37:36,160
 i sad evo,

1618
01:37:36,160 --> 01:37:38,140
 ovo što je Zadnje Milanović rekao,

1619
01:37:38,140 --> 01:37:40,580
 bi bilo apsolutno sukladno tome,

1620
01:37:40,580 --> 01:37:41,220
 zato što

1621
01:37:41,220 --> 01:37:43,300
 ako je Izrael...

1622
01:37:43,940 --> 01:37:46,180
 mislite, na ovu predsjednikovu izjavu...

1623
01:37:46,180 --> 01:37:47,480
 Predsjednikovu izjavu da Izrael

1624
01:37:47,480 --> 01:37:51,360
 naoružava Srbiju protiv Hrvatske.

1625
01:37:51,360 --> 01:37:53,680
 To vam je opet ovo nastojanje

1626
01:37:53,680 --> 01:37:55,320
 Britanskog carstva da pokrene

1627
01:37:55,320 --> 01:37:56,960
 rat na Balkanu,

1628
01:37:56,960 --> 01:37:59,620
 kao drugi front u sukobu

1629
01:37:59,620 --> 01:38:01,060
 Zapada protiv Rusija

1630
01:38:01,060 --> 01:38:05,260
 i da se treba nekako

1631
01:38:05,260 --> 01:38:06,760
 nahuškat opet

1632
01:38:06,760 --> 01:38:08,020
 Srbe protiv Hrvata,

1633
01:38:08,020 --> 01:38:09,540
 Hrvatsku protiv Srbije

1634
01:38:09,540 --> 01:38:10,480
 i tako dalje.

1635
01:38:10,480 --> 01:38:12,460
 I sad,

1636
01:38:12,460 --> 01:38:14,340
 ako je Izrael

1637
01:38:14,340 --> 01:38:17,220
 pod kontrolom

1638
01:38:17,220 --> 01:38:18,320
 Britanskog carstva,

1639
01:38:18,320 --> 01:38:19,640
 što smo spomenuli,

1640
01:38:19,640 --> 01:38:21,480
 da je cijeli taj cionistički projekt,

1641
01:38:21,480 --> 01:38:23,840
 proizvod

1642
01:38:23,840 --> 01:38:25,980
 Britanskog imperija,

1643
01:38:25,980 --> 01:38:29,620
 onda to opet ima smisla.

1644
01:38:29,620 --> 01:38:30,500
 To je taj...

1645
01:38:30,500 --> 01:38:32,060
 Onda vi opet nešto povezuje?

1646
01:38:32,060 --> 01:38:33,420
 To je opet isti sukob.

1647
01:38:33,420 --> 01:38:35,680
 To je opet isti sukob

1648
01:38:35,680 --> 01:38:37,620
 koji se sada i nama nameče,

1649
01:38:37,620 --> 01:38:39,980
 ne zato što smo mi njima

1650
01:38:39,980 --> 01:38:41,020
 osobito važni,

1651
01:38:41,020 --> 01:38:43,460
 niti im je Srbija osobito važna,

1652
01:38:43,460 --> 01:38:45,700
 nego isto kako su upotrebili Srbiju

1653
01:38:45,700 --> 01:38:46,980
 da se sukobe s Turcima

1654
01:38:46,980 --> 01:38:50,200
 tokom Balkanskih ratova,

1655
01:38:50,200 --> 01:38:52,880
 tako sada možda žele upotrebiti Srbiju

1656
01:38:52,880 --> 01:38:55,940
 da se zarati protiv Hrvatske.

1657
01:38:55,940 --> 01:38:58,160
 I nije im ni to toliko važno

1658
01:38:58,160 --> 01:38:59,020
 koliko im je važno

1659
01:38:59,020 --> 01:38:59,940
 da se onda uvuče

1660
01:38:59,940 --> 01:39:01,960
 NATO u rat na Balkanu,

1661
01:39:01,960 --> 01:39:03,400
 zato su nastavili

1662
01:39:03,400 --> 01:39:04,500
 u savez s Albanijom,

1663
01:39:04,500 --> 01:39:05,080
 s Bugarskom,

1664
01:39:05,080 --> 01:39:06,500
 s kojima mi pak ništa nemamo,

1665
01:39:06,500 --> 01:39:08,280
 ne vidi zašto bi mi imali

1666
01:39:08,280 --> 01:39:09,340
 vojni savez s njima,

1667
01:39:09,340 --> 01:39:10,940
 osim u ovom,

1668
01:39:10,940 --> 01:39:13,160
 u okviru ovih planova

1669
01:39:13,160 --> 01:39:14,340
 i da se onda,

1670
01:39:14,340 --> 01:39:15,300
 kad je recimo

1671
01:39:15,300 --> 01:39:17,200
 NATO uvučen

1672
01:39:17,200 --> 01:39:19,500
 u rat protiv Srbije,

1673
01:39:19,500 --> 01:39:20,720
 e onda ni Rusija

1674
01:39:20,720 --> 01:39:22,040
 ne može ostati pasivno,

1675
01:39:22,040 --> 01:39:23,760
 kao pasivni promatrač

1676
01:39:23,760 --> 01:39:27,020
 i tako se onda opet Rusija nameće

1677
01:39:27,020 --> 01:39:29,220
 drugi front.

1678
01:39:29,220 --> 01:39:34,220
 A to je vrlo, vrlo slični scenarijo

1679
01:39:34,220 --> 01:39:37,480
 kao 1914.

1680
01:39:38,220 --> 01:39:39,740
 znači tu onda postoji rizik

1681
01:39:39,740 --> 01:39:42,520
 da opet imamo generalni rat

1682
01:39:42,520 --> 01:39:45,500
 na cijelom evropskom kontinentu,

1683
01:39:45,500 --> 01:39:47,020
 koji je prije sto godina

1684
01:39:47,020 --> 01:39:49,940
 završio sa 20 miliona mrtvih

1685
01:39:49,940 --> 01:39:51,680
 i 40 miliona ukupno

1686
01:39:51,680 --> 01:39:53,780
 ranjenih i nestalih,

1687
01:39:53,780 --> 01:39:56,040
 a sad bi moglo biti puno gore.

1688
01:39:56,840 --> 01:39:57,860
 Međutim, njima je to ok,

1689
01:39:57,860 --> 01:39:58,400
 jer oni

1690
01:39:58,400 --> 01:40:01,880
 kroz rat ovi uvijek profitiraju.

1691
01:40:01,880 --> 01:40:02,460
 Pa da,

1692
01:40:02,460 --> 01:40:04,180
 više je profita kroz rat

1693
01:40:04,180 --> 01:40:04,880
 nego kroz mir.

1694
01:40:04,880 --> 01:40:05,960
 Da, apsolutno.

1695
01:40:05,960 --> 01:40:07,500
 I sad, znate, bilo bi,

1696
01:40:07,500 --> 01:40:09,820
 to je odgovor na pitanje

1697
01:40:09,820 --> 01:40:11,160
 tko nam trese staklenku.

1698
01:40:11,160 --> 01:40:13,120
 I onda umjesto da smo...

1699
01:40:13,120 --> 01:40:14,900
 Već ova vaša antologijska izjava,

1700
01:40:14,900 --> 01:40:15,400
 svi kažu

1701
01:40:15,400 --> 01:40:17,300
 kako je Krajner objasnio

1702
01:40:17,300 --> 01:40:18,900
 tko nam trese staklenku.

1703
01:40:18,900 --> 01:40:19,460
 Da.

1704
01:40:19,460 --> 01:40:21,640
 Da, učit ćete u anale YouTube-a,

1705
01:40:21,640 --> 01:40:23,160
 odnosno, odnosno podcasta.

1706
01:40:23,160 --> 01:40:24,780
 Da, ali gledajte,

1707
01:40:24,780 --> 01:40:25,920
 znate, to je važno

1708
01:40:25,920 --> 01:40:27,880
 i to ne govori ja samo za Hrvate.

1709
01:40:27,880 --> 01:40:29,260
 O tome trebaju razmišljati

1710
01:40:29,260 --> 01:40:31,260
 i muslimani u Bosni,

1711
01:40:31,260 --> 01:40:32,660
 i Srbi, i Crnogorci,

1712
01:40:32,660 --> 01:40:33,020
 i svi,

1713
01:40:33,020 --> 01:40:33,900
 jer smo,

1714
01:40:33,900 --> 01:40:35,600
 svi smo mi u toj staklenci.

1715
01:40:35,600 --> 01:40:36,940
 Svi mi tu živimo

1716
01:40:36,940 --> 01:40:37,640
 gde smo,

1717
01:40:37,640 --> 01:40:39,060
 na ovim prostorima

1718
01:40:39,060 --> 01:40:40,860
 gde je neizbježno komunicirano,

1719
01:40:40,860 --> 01:40:42,460
 komuniciramo,

1720
01:40:42,460 --> 01:40:43,560
 premreženi smo

1721
01:40:43,560 --> 01:40:45,120
 i moramo znat

1722
01:40:45,120 --> 01:40:49,400
 da nas se u sukob gura.

1723
01:40:49,400 --> 01:40:53,120
 Da nam je ta zamka

1724
01:40:53,120 --> 01:40:54,400
 u biti stalno...

1725
01:40:54,920 --> 01:40:59,380
 Samo je pitanje kad će neko uspjet fitilj pripalit

1726
01:40:59,380 --> 01:41:01,220
 na dobar način.

1727
01:41:01,220 --> 01:41:02,720
 Ja se nadam da baš i neće.

1728
01:41:02,720 --> 01:41:04,980
 I znači, umjesto da budemo obsjednuti

1729
01:41:04,980 --> 01:41:07,140
 šta se desilo prije 80 godina,

1730
01:41:07,140 --> 01:41:09,080
 trebali bi biti obsjednuti s time

1731
01:41:09,080 --> 01:41:12,140
 šta se može desiti u idućih 10 godina,

1732
01:41:12,140 --> 01:41:14,800
 jer to onda definira budućnost

1733
01:41:14,800 --> 01:41:19,920
 koju će na kraju krajeva proživljavati naša djeca.

1734
01:41:19,920 --> 01:41:23,660
 Da li da završe kao žrtve rata

1735
01:41:23,660 --> 01:41:26,440
 na nekom, u nekim blatnjavim rovovima

1736
01:41:26,440 --> 01:41:28,720
 ili da živimo u miru, u blagostanju.

1737
01:41:28,720 --> 01:41:31,700
 Ja mislim da je to naš izbor

1738
01:41:31,700 --> 01:41:33,720
 i zato moramo biti obsjednuti

1739
01:41:33,720 --> 01:41:35,500
 s onima šta nam staklenku tresu,

1740
01:41:35,500 --> 01:41:38,540
 a ne sa drugim mravima

1741
01:41:38,540 --> 01:41:39,880
 koji su to isto staklenke.

1742
01:41:39,880 --> 01:41:41,740
 U biti, sa tim drugim mravima

1743
01:41:41,740 --> 01:41:43,020
 bi se trebali dogovoriti.

1744
01:41:43,020 --> 01:41:47,000
 Kad nam pro tresu staklenku pazi,

1745
01:41:47,000 --> 01:41:50,600
 kontroliraj se, ne reagiraj odmah,

1746
01:41:50,600 --> 01:41:51,780
 ne budi impulzivan,

1747
01:41:51,780 --> 01:41:55,420
 stani na loptu i idemo malo razmisliti

1748
01:41:55,420 --> 01:41:57,020
 o svemu prije nego što krenemo

1749
01:41:57,020 --> 01:41:59,100
 u tučnjavu i pucnjavu.

1750
01:41:59,100 --> 01:42:01,140
 Može još jedno pitanje?

1751
01:42:01,140 --> 01:42:02,220
 Apsolutno.

1752
01:42:03,300 --> 01:42:04,340
 Nakon ovog ćete,

1753
01:42:04,340 --> 01:42:06,760
 nećete mi više htjeti doći.

1754
01:42:06,760 --> 01:42:10,960
 Rekla sam da ste vani živjeli.

1755
01:42:10,960 --> 01:42:14,160
 Nabrojali smo zemlje.

1756
01:42:14,160 --> 01:42:14,980
 Imali zemlje,

1757
01:42:14,980 --> 01:42:16,880
 sad ovo ne ispadne patetično.

1758
01:42:16,880 --> 01:42:18,280
 Kako se, kad uspoređujete

1759
01:42:18,280 --> 01:42:19,300
 taj život vani

1760
01:42:19,300 --> 01:42:20,200
 i ovaj u Hrvatskoj

1761
01:42:20,200 --> 01:42:21,840
 sad kad dođete doma,

1762
01:42:21,840 --> 01:42:24,120
 gdje se bolje živi?

1763
01:42:24,120 --> 01:42:27,340
 E, sad ću vam dat citat

1764
01:42:27,340 --> 01:42:28,000
 mog sina.

1765
01:42:28,000 --> 01:42:28,660
 Ajde.

1766
01:42:28,660 --> 01:42:30,760
 Koji danas ima 15 godina.

1767
01:42:30,760 --> 01:42:32,220
 Ima danas 15 godina,

1768
01:42:32,220 --> 01:42:32,880
 ali je imao

1769
01:42:32,880 --> 01:42:33,940
 ne danas,

1770
01:42:33,940 --> 01:42:35,100
 ne da mu je danas rođena,

1771
01:42:35,100 --> 01:42:36,520
 nego sad je imao 15 godina,

1772
01:42:36,520 --> 01:42:38,500
 ali ova izjava

1773
01:42:38,500 --> 01:42:40,260
 dolazi kad imao 8 godina.

1774
01:42:40,260 --> 01:42:40,600
 Znači,

1775
01:42:40,600 --> 01:42:41,140
 mislim vam,

1776
01:42:41,140 --> 01:42:44,040
 da vam dam ideju

1777
01:42:44,040 --> 01:42:45,680
 od kuda je on došao

1778
01:42:45,680 --> 01:42:47,080
 i gdje je on došao.

1779
01:42:47,840 --> 01:42:49,860
 on se rodi u Monaku.

1780
01:42:49,860 --> 01:42:52,480
 Mi smo onda živjeli,

1781
01:42:52,480 --> 01:42:53,500
 znači onda sam bio

1782
01:42:53,500 --> 01:42:55,660
 u tim investicijskim krugovima,

1783
01:42:55,660 --> 01:42:57,100
 ja sam relativno dobro živio,

1784
01:42:57,100 --> 01:42:58,320
 mi smo živjeli u zgradi

1785
01:42:58,320 --> 01:43:00,220
 u Marini,

1786
01:43:00,220 --> 01:43:01,740
 u Monaku,

1787
01:43:01,740 --> 01:43:02,880
 koja je ovako gledala

1788
01:43:02,880 --> 01:43:04,460
 ravno na more.

1789
01:43:06,120 --> 01:43:07,800
 meni je susjeda u zgradi

1790
01:43:07,800 --> 01:43:09,960
 bila ova princeza Stefani.

1791
01:43:09,960 --> 01:43:13,440
 Iz kuće smo imali

1792
01:43:13,440 --> 01:43:15,520
 direktan izlaz u park,

1793
01:43:15,520 --> 01:43:18,520
 zgrada imala svoj privatni bazen

1794
01:43:18,520 --> 01:43:20,620
 na lukobranu.

1795
01:43:20,760 --> 01:43:21,560
 znači,

1796
01:43:21,560 --> 01:43:25,460
 nije da se u gazi rodio,

1797
01:43:25,460 --> 01:43:27,080
 znači nije da se rodio

1798
01:43:27,080 --> 01:43:27,880
 u nekom teškom,

1799
01:43:27,880 --> 01:43:32,520
 znači to je njemu bila referenca,

1800
01:43:32,520 --> 01:43:33,320
 to je bio svijet

1801
01:43:33,320 --> 01:43:34,960
 koje on znao.

1802
01:43:34,960 --> 01:43:37,560
 I onda jedan dan

1803
01:43:37,560 --> 01:43:39,240
 smo tako došli u opatiju

1804
01:43:39,240 --> 01:43:41,320
 i to je bio neko gluho vrijeme,

1805
01:43:41,320 --> 01:43:42,800
 deseti mjesec.

1806
01:43:42,800 --> 01:43:45,520
 Niš, niti plaža, niti sunce,

1807
01:43:45,520 --> 01:43:46,600
 onako.

1808
01:43:46,600 --> 01:43:49,140
 Došli smo posjetiti Nonića

1809
01:43:49,140 --> 01:43:51,080
 i spustimo se ja

1810
01:43:51,080 --> 01:43:52,480
 i on dolje do šetnice

1811
01:43:52,480 --> 01:43:53,320
 na plažu

1812
01:43:53,320 --> 01:43:56,860
 i on onako stoji na plaži

1813
01:43:56,860 --> 01:43:58,980
 i gleda prema moru

1814
01:43:58,980 --> 01:43:59,620
 zamišljeno

1815
01:43:59,620 --> 01:44:00,500
 i kaže meni

1816
01:44:00,500 --> 01:44:02,260
 tata, znaš,

1817
01:44:02,260 --> 01:44:05,260
 baš je dobro da smo došli.

1818
01:44:05,260 --> 01:44:07,540
 Ja kažem, zašto, Itan?

1819
01:44:07,540 --> 01:44:08,100
 On kaže,

1820
01:44:08,100 --> 01:44:11,520
 pa ništa podsjetilo mi je

1821
01:44:11,520 --> 01:44:12,460
 da je ovdje bolje.

1822
01:44:12,460 --> 01:44:15,120
 Ajmo kažem, Itan,

1823
01:44:15,120 --> 01:44:16,220
 šta je ovdje bolje?

1824
01:44:16,220 --> 01:44:18,900
 On meni kaže, sve.

1825
01:44:19,140 --> 01:44:21,600
 Razumijete?

1826
01:44:21,600 --> 01:44:22,100
 Da.

1827
01:44:22,100 --> 01:44:25,240
 Sad, kako da vam ja interpretiraš

1828
01:44:25,240 --> 01:44:27,000
 taj jedan osam godišnjak,

1829
01:44:27,000 --> 01:44:29,700
 zašto on kaže da je ovdje sve bolje?

1830
01:44:29,700 --> 01:44:33,840
 On ne mora brinuti ni o zdravstvenom osiguranju,

1831
01:44:33,840 --> 01:44:35,320
 ni o plaćama, ni o penziji,

1832
01:44:35,320 --> 01:44:35,940
 ni ti o ništa.

1833
01:44:35,940 --> 01:44:38,220
 On naprosto vidi svijet kakav mu se,

1834
01:44:38,220 --> 01:44:39,860
 kakav je pred njim.

1835
01:44:40,860 --> 01:44:41,260
 i sad,

1836
01:44:41,260 --> 01:44:43,220
 ovdje,

1837
01:44:43,220 --> 01:44:44,040
 ja ne znam,

1838
01:44:44,040 --> 01:44:45,800
 neko podneblje je,

1839
01:44:45,800 --> 01:44:47,260
 pitom,

1840
01:44:47,260 --> 01:44:48,520
 moja bivša supruga,

1841
01:44:48,520 --> 01:44:49,540
 koja je amerikanka,

1842
01:44:49,540 --> 01:44:51,740
 je bila zaljubljena u Hrvatsku.

1843
01:44:51,740 --> 01:44:52,320
 Ona je,

1844
01:44:52,320 --> 01:44:54,680
 ona je mene tjerala da se mi vratimo.

1845
01:44:54,680 --> 01:44:56,400
 Ona kad je tu došla,

1846
01:44:56,400 --> 01:44:57,980
 kad je upoznala ljude ovdje,

1847
01:44:57,980 --> 01:45:00,500
 kad je upoznala malo Hrvatsku,

1848
01:45:00,500 --> 01:45:03,040
 ona je mene preklijala da se mi vratimo.

1849
01:45:03,040 --> 01:45:04,080
 što ja nisam mogo,

1850
01:45:04,080 --> 01:45:06,820
 jer meni je posao bio tamo.

1851
01:45:06,820 --> 01:45:09,180
 Ja sam se morao nacrtati u uredu svako jutro

1852
01:45:09,180 --> 01:45:11,160
 i bilo je nerealno,

1853
01:45:11,160 --> 01:45:12,180
 ali eto,

1854
01:45:12,180 --> 01:45:13,440
 znači,

1855
01:45:13,440 --> 01:45:13,920
 gledajte,

1856
01:45:13,920 --> 01:45:14,960
 ja sam živio u Americi,

1857
01:45:14,960 --> 01:45:15,640
 u Švicarskoj,

1858
01:45:15,640 --> 01:45:16,820
 u Venecueli,

1859
01:45:16,820 --> 01:45:18,660
 proput toga sam jako puno svijeta

1860
01:45:18,660 --> 01:45:21,480
 i Tursku obalu,

1861
01:45:21,480 --> 01:45:22,380
 i Grčku obalu,

1862
01:45:22,380 --> 01:45:23,580
 i na Karibima,

1863
01:45:23,580 --> 01:45:25,020
 nisam bio na svim otocima,

1864
01:45:25,020 --> 01:45:25,700
 ne mogu reći,

1865
01:45:25,700 --> 01:45:27,240
 ali sam bio na puno njih.

1866
01:45:27,240 --> 01:45:30,620
 I mene srce uvijek vuče nazad u Hrvatsku.

1867
01:45:30,620 --> 01:45:31,840
 A ja nisam nostalgičar,

1868
01:45:31,880 --> 01:45:33,280
 ja ne patim od nostalgije,

1869
01:45:33,280 --> 01:45:36,660
 nego ja sam naprosto

1870
01:45:36,660 --> 01:45:39,380
 dosta različitih kuhinja

1871
01:45:39,380 --> 01:45:40,720
 probao da si kažem

1872
01:45:40,720 --> 01:45:42,620
 naša mi je najbolja

1873
01:45:42,620 --> 01:45:43,740
 i znam da nisam jedini.

1874
01:45:43,740 --> 01:45:45,760
 Jer ima jako puno Hrvata

1875
01:45:45,760 --> 01:45:46,760
 koji žive vani,

1876
01:45:46,760 --> 01:45:52,380
 koji se žele vratiti.

1877
01:45:52,380 --> 01:45:54,560
 A upoznao sam čak i Hrvata

1878
01:45:54,560 --> 01:45:56,580
 koji su se rodili izvan Hrvatske,

1879
01:45:56,580 --> 01:45:57,840
 kao moja djeca,

1880
01:45:57,840 --> 01:46:01,060
 koji isto se žele vratiti.

1881
01:46:01,880 --> 01:46:03,120
 Znači ja sam jednom

1882
01:46:03,120 --> 01:46:04,520
 išao sam jedriti.

1883
01:46:04,520 --> 01:46:05,380
 Bio mi je skiper,

1884
01:46:05,380 --> 01:46:06,200
 nekakav tako,

1885
01:46:06,200 --> 01:46:07,220
 taj dečko što je.

1886
01:46:07,220 --> 01:46:09,060
 Jedva je Hrvatski govorio,

1887
01:46:09,060 --> 01:46:11,100
 naučio je prvi moj jezik,

1888
01:46:11,100 --> 01:46:13,060
 njemački u Švicarskoj.

1889
01:46:13,060 --> 01:46:17,160
 Ali sve, sve, sve želi da se vrati.

1890
01:46:17,160 --> 01:46:18,640
 Ne da se vrati,

1891
01:46:18,640 --> 01:46:19,700
 tamo se rodio,

1892
01:46:19,700 --> 01:46:20,500
 tamo je odraso,

1893
01:46:20,500 --> 01:46:22,180
 ali došao u Hrvatsku,

1894
01:46:22,700 --> 01:46:24,380
 osjetio da su mu tu korijeni

1895
01:46:24,380 --> 01:46:26,100
 i rekao mi je,

1896
01:46:26,100 --> 01:46:26,420
 čuj,

1897
01:46:26,420 --> 01:46:28,600
 hoću ovdje živjeti,

1898
01:46:28,600 --> 01:46:29,800
 hoću se ovdje vratiti.

1899
01:46:29,800 --> 01:46:31,160
 Tako da,

1900
01:46:31,160 --> 01:46:33,720
 sve ovo što,

1901
01:46:33,720 --> 01:46:35,660
 kad živite ovdje,

1902
01:46:35,660 --> 01:46:37,380
 uzimate zdravo za gotovo,

1903
01:46:37,380 --> 01:46:41,100
 poslije shvatite da je,

1904
01:46:41,100 --> 01:46:42,080
 da je u biti,

1905
01:46:42,080 --> 01:46:43,980
 jedan čudesan,

1906
01:46:43,980 --> 01:46:44,920
 čudesan dar,

1907
01:46:45,160 --> 01:46:46,780
 da ovo imamo.

1908
01:46:46,780 --> 01:46:53,220
 Trebali bi se malo bolje o tome brinuti

1909
01:46:53,220 --> 01:46:57,180
 i malo to sa više srca i duša baštiniti,

1910
01:46:57,180 --> 01:47:01,320
 rađe nego biti povodljivi za ovim,

1911
01:47:01,320 --> 01:47:01,980
 znate,

1912
01:47:01,980 --> 01:47:09,200
 Brisel i Strasburg i London i New York,

1913
01:47:09,200 --> 01:47:10,960
 sve to o čemu ljudi sanjaju,

1914
01:47:10,960 --> 01:47:12,560
 jer misle da je tamo bolje,

1915
01:47:12,560 --> 01:47:12,860
 ali nije.

1916
01:47:12,860 --> 01:47:13,620
 Ja tamo živim,

1917
01:47:13,620 --> 01:47:14,220
 nije bolje.

1918
01:47:15,160 --> 01:47:16,240
 Hoćete se vratiti?

1919
01:47:16,240 --> 01:47:18,480
 Znate šta,

1920
01:47:18,480 --> 01:47:21,100
 meni su djeca vani,

1921
01:47:21,100 --> 01:47:22,620
 ja moram ostati u svojoj djeca,

1922
01:47:22,620 --> 01:47:25,380
 jer su ja pre mali da ih prepustim,

1923
01:47:25,380 --> 01:47:28,280
 sebe samima,

1924
01:47:28,280 --> 01:47:29,460
 ali u dogledno vrijeme,

1925
01:47:29,460 --> 01:47:30,200
 apsolutno da.

1926
01:47:30,200 --> 01:47:32,300
 Čekamo vas onda,

1927
01:47:32,300 --> 01:47:33,900
 razširenih rupu.

1928
01:47:33,900 --> 01:47:35,440
 Jedva čekam da dođem.

1929
01:47:35,440 --> 01:47:36,960
 Hvala vam.

1930
01:47:36,960 --> 01:47:38,940
 Hvala vam na pozivu,

1931
01:47:38,940 --> 01:47:40,300
 puno ste me tvari pitali,

1932
01:47:40,300 --> 01:47:41,820
 tako da nisam Badava dolazio.

1933
01:47:41,820 --> 01:47:45,020
 Nikad ne dođete Badava,

1934
01:47:45,160 --> 01:47:46,620
 nadam da se...

1935
01:47:46,620 --> 01:47:48,980
 Ne, ne, uvijek mi je veselje

1936
01:47:48,980 --> 01:47:50,220
 i drago mi je

1937
01:47:50,220 --> 01:47:53,120
 i zahvalan sam na pozivu

1938
01:47:53,120 --> 01:47:55,620
 i zahvalan sam na tome što

1939
01:47:55,620 --> 01:47:58,000
 ljudi to i gledaju i slušaju,

1940
01:47:58,000 --> 01:48:00,200
 znači da razmišljaju,

1941
01:48:00,200 --> 01:48:00,960
 znači da smo

1942
01:48:00,960 --> 01:48:04,160
 na dobrom putu,

1943
01:48:04,160 --> 01:48:05,480
 jer toga nekad nije bilo.

1944
01:48:05,700 --> 01:48:07,160
